https://leetcode.com/problems/valid-anagram/submissions/1852229481/

class Solution {
public:
    bool isAnagram(string s, string t) 
    {
        vector<int> freq(26,0); //why because ascii of a is 97 ,98,99 till 127. if we subtract -'a' from each then we need only arr of size 26

        for(auto ele:s) //increment count of each char of s in freq array
        {
            freq[ele-'a']++;
        }

        for(auto ele:t) //decrement count of each char of t in freq array 
        {
            freq[ele-'a']--;
        }

        for(auto ele:freq)
        {
            if(ele != 0)
            {
                return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
};

1️⃣ Time Complexity

Loop through s → O(s)

Loop through t → O(t)   Total is : o(s) + o(t)

Loop through freq (size 26) → O(26) ≈ O(1)

✅ Total: O(n)

Where n = s.size() = t.size().

2️⃣ Space Complexity

freq array of size 26 → O(26) → O(1)

No other extra space proportional to n.

✅ Total: O(1)
